709515f-c.title: Manhattan: 6th Avenue - 46th Avenue
709515f-c.text:
Sixth Avenue, west side, north from W. 45t' Street. The bu'ld-
ings adjoining the corner are to be demolished for a new structure
to house a new ''Automat;'' view 2 is limited to these. No. 3 is
a later view of the same location. Note the Rockefeller Center
buildings at the right. The ''E1'' line in the center of the Avenue
will be torn down in 1939.

View 3: March 22, 1934
